data.description: Welcome to this fairly new built 3 bedrooms, 2 bath home in the desirable Woodland Park Subdivision.  Pulling up to the home you will notice the plush landscaping and paver driveway.  Step inside and you are greeted with wood-like tile throughout the main living areas.  French doors lead the way to front office that can easily be made into a 4th Bedroom.  You will enjoy preparing meals in the spacious kithcen featuring quartz counter tops stainless steel appliances, closet pantry with plenty and cabinet space.  The kithcen overlooks the family room that has sliding door access to the covered lanai. The huge primary ensuite  features tray ceilings, walk-in closet, dual sinks, soaking tub w/ separate shower stall. The additional bedrooms share a full bath.  Woodland Park plans call for a community pavilion, pool, multipurpose field, playground and several passive parks. Several wetland habitats are preserved as conservation areas within the community, adding to its natural beauty and appeal. Woodland Park is within minutes of Medical City, Orlando theme parks, the Orlando International Airport and other job centers. Groceries, retail, banking, restaurants, movie theaters and other essential services are just a short drive from the community. Good schools are within walking distance. And major transportation corridors are easily accessed.
